242
00:22:27,113 --> 00:22:28,944
I can't take it anymore.

243
00:22:29,248 --> 00:22:31,876
That girl just didn't come from nowhere.

244
00:22:32,418 --> 00:22:36,115
Jia-Chien's a perfect blend
of you and her mother.

245
00:22:37,023 --> 00:22:39,753
Her mother's stubbornness and willfulness.

246
00:22:39,859 --> 00:22:42,327
And the pickiness and pomposity...

247
00:22:42,829 --> 00:22:44,820
...come straight from you!

248
00:22:46,099 --> 00:22:48,659
I think I know her better than you do.

249
00:22:49,869 --> 00:22:53,202
